OL,3,CNo plans to make Guernsey Election
OL,4,Cmanifesto booklet more accessible
OL,6,FAhead of the last island-wide ballot
OL,7,Fin 2020, the comprehensive booklet was
OL,8,Fmore than two hundred pages long and
OL,9,Fwritten in a small font.
OL,11,FGerry Platt is visually impaired and
OL,12,Fhas only 20% vision due to having a
OL,13,Fcondition called birdshot
OL,14,Fchorioretinopathy.
OL,16,FHe cannot read the lengthy document
OL,17,Fand says he has to rely on others to
OL,18,Fhelp him work out who to vote for.
