OL,6,FGerry adds: "I'm in a more advanced
OL,7,Fsituation simply because my eyesight
OL,8,Fhas now deteriorated to a level that
OL,9,Fmy wife fortunately helps me to read
OL,10,Fall the information and mail that we
OL,11,Fget."
OL,13,FBarry Bartlett faces a similar dilemma
OL,14,Fas he has macular degeneration.
OL,16,FHe explains: "Bear in mind there are a
OL,17,Fnumber of people that have eyesight
OL,18,Fproblems, the print is small for a
OL,19,Fstart and the font is probably the
OL,20,Fthinnest one you can have."
