OL,4,Cmanifesto booklet more accessible
OL,6,F"They need to be taking that into
OL,7,Fconsideration, text that's easy to
OL,8,Fread and the right size. Actually, in
OL,9,Fsome ways, that part of the difference
OL,10,Fcandidates can look to have between
OL,11,Feach other.
OL,13,F"There was a concern that the existing
OL,14,Fgovernment shouldn't interfere in the
OL,15,Felectoral process."
OL,17,FFor the dyslexic community on the
OL,18,Fisland, it can also be a struggle for
OL,19,Fthem to work out who they want to be
OL,20,Ftheir next representatives if the
OL,21,Fformatting is not accessible.
