OL,3,CNo plans to make Guernsey Election
OL,4,Cmanifesto booklet more accessible
OL,6,FTeresa O'Hara, Centre Manager of the
OL,7,FDyslexia Day Centre, says: "You need
OL,8,Fto keep it just to the point and in a
OL,9,Fvery plain text, no fancy backgrounds.
OL,11,F"Preferably, if they can have it on
OL,12,Foff-white paper or light pastel paper,
OL,13,Fjust not white paper because the glare
OL,14,Fof the print and the paper can effect
OL,15,Fdyslexic people."
OL,17,FFollowing the introduction of island-
OL,18,Fwide voting in 2018, islanders no
OL,19,Flonger choose candidates in
OL,20,Fconstituencies determined by the
OL,21,Fparish in which they live.
